Currently there is no class to handle dates, hence there should
be a utility class to validate and manage date format.

A DateUtil class is added to help check if given dates follow a
specific yyyy-MM-dd format. A DateOfBirth class is also added,
which utilises the DateUtil class, that will serve as a parameter
for the Person class.

The DateUtil class was updated to contain only methods to be used
and not for storing assigned dates. Gender and Nric classes are
added to contain logic for the supported parameters when adding
patients.

The Person class was updated to store the new parameters and the
logic of checking whether two person are the same was changed to
compare their Nric instead
